{"componentChunkName":"component---src-templates-post-js","path":"/posts/vy7af38ydcn5qxbl/","result":{"data":{"sitePage":null},"pageContext":{"url":"posts/vy7af38ydcn5qxbl","relativePath":"posts/vy7af38ydcn5qxbl","frontmatter":{"title":"纯技术式的英语学习方式","stackbit_url_path":"posts/vy7af38ydcn5qxbl","date":"2024-01-25T12:31:47","excerpt":"","tags":[],"categories":[],"template":"post"},"html":"<p>时常懊恼，从初中一年级开始学习英语，到大学毕业，学习了整整 10 年英语！然而工作中碰到需要英语的场合，却仍然开不了口。<br />2010 年我加入一家软件外包公司，客户是国外的，需要用英语和客户沟通，于是我又去公司附近的“昂立英语”报了一个英语学习班，老师是一个美国人，一共只有 3 个学生。怎么说呢，全程尬聊，非常艰难，上课用的是 Top Notch 那套教材，我感觉又回到了学生时代，感觉个人兴趣不大，因此坚持了一个学期，就放弃了。<br />后来又去英孚教育上班了，公司的福利，可以免费学习半年的成人英语课程。课程类型丰富多样，似乎更有趣，然而我还是没有坚持下来，去了几个星期就放弃了。原因是大班课上，经常是中教，或者有时候也是外教，但上课风格总是老师没讲几句，就让我们分组讨论。而互相讨论的对象，都是一帮英语不好的学生。小班课人少一点，但很难排到，除了要完成多少多少节大课之外，还需要做很多练习题，这时就又像是回到了学生时代。由于我不怎么做题，因此没上过几节小班课。上大班课时，我只听老师前面讲点东西，后面就一直走神了。<br />我很懊恼，我在英语学习上投入了太多时间，然而一要开口，就不知道说啥！这种感觉，就像是基金定投，说好的长期回报呢？没看到，只看到跌跌不休。又像是在玩 A 股，十几年的投入，到最后只是被套牢，并没有收益。<br />直到最近，我发现，所谓的英语不好，其实只是个表象。我发现自己并不是在需要讲英语的场合开不了口，而只是纯粹地“<strong>开不了口</strong>”。我发现自己的问题是，1、<strong>不会聊天</strong>；2、<strong>没有逻辑</strong>。这两点让我根本不会讲话，和别人也是聊不下去。当然，在需要讲英语的场合，让这两个问题暴露得更加彻底。<br />同时，我发现，在某些场合，我还是可以开口的，比如讨论一些具体要求的问题，而不是聊天，我仍然能说几句。并且在这些场合，我发现了一些纯粹技术上的小技巧，今天在这里分享出来。\n<a name=ruV4p></a></p>\n<h1>对于具体问题，多约视频会议</h1>\n<p>因为人在国内，所以并没有太多机会和外国人面对面进行交流，尤其是对于不会聊天的人来说，面对面的交流更加难得。因为就算碰到以英语为母语的人，如果没有任何交集，没有任何具体的事情需要沟通，那么交流就不会发生。有了具体问题，人家不一定在国内，所以就可以约视频聊天。\n<a name=oHX2J></a></p>\n<h2>CKEditor 和 Strapi</h2>\n<p>如果看过我分享的技术博文，会发现我写过一些 CKEditor 和 Strapi 的文章（最新的一篇是两者结合起来：《<a href=\"%5Bhttps://zhuanlan.zhihu.com/p/674864877%5D(https://zhuanlan.zhihu.com/p/674864877)\">借助 Bedrock SDK，全面释放内容生产力 - Jeff Tian的文章 - 知乎</a> 》），我最近就转念一想，为什么碰到问题后，不直接找他们团队的人聊呢？于是我很快实践了一下，分别约了 CKEditor 和 Strapi 团队的客户经理各聊了半小时，询问了一些许可证的问题。由于是实际碰到的问题，效果还不错，全程没有冷场或者尬聊的情况。遗憾的是，这两个产品的许可证都很贵，我目前还承担不起，所以有些高级功能使用不了（不过我都试用过了，非常棒！未来如果可以把它们包装成产品卖出去的话，可以考虑购买他们的许可证）。\n<a name=t7W3F></a></p>\n<h2>Code Review</h2>\n<p>除了这种情况，我还会在 Code Review 环节，快速约人视频一下，这样不仅提高代码复审效率，还顺便练习一下英语，最重要的是，还能拉近同事间的个人关系，增加彼此的信任。\n<a name=Err49></a></p>\n<h2>LinkedIn</h2>\n<p>有意思的是，当我发现这个方法后，我还收到了某些视频博主的邀请，就解决某个技术问题一起录个视频，这非常有意思，后面我会将这些视频也分享出来。<br /><span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 590px; \"\n    >\n      <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 97.97297297297297%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block; transition: opacity 0.5s 0.5s; pointer-events: none;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"image.png\"\n        title=\"image.png\"\n        src=\"/static/288b530fef2ec507b72c7282676db54b/fcda8/1706185301473-b7155f04-3bb6-492b-b03f-ff97d4686d72.png\"\n        srcset=\"/static/288b530fef2ec507b72c7282676db54b/12f09/1706185301473-b7155f04-3bb6-492b-b03f-ff97d4686d72.png 148w,\n/static/288b530fef2ec507b72c7282676db54b/e4a3f/1706185301473-b7155f04-3bb6-492b-b03f-ff97d4686d72.png 295w,\n/static/288b530fef2ec507b72c7282676db54b/fcda8/1706185301473-b7155f04-3bb6-492b-b03f-ff97d4686d72.png 590w,\n/static/288b530fef2ec507b72c7282676db54b/efc66/1706185301473-b7155f04-3bb6-492b-b03f-ff97d4686d72.png 885w,\n/static/288b530fef2ec507b72c7282676db54b/c83ae/1706185301473-b7155f04-3bb6-492b-b03f-ff97d4686d72.png 1180w,\n/static/288b530fef2ec507b72c7282676db54b/016a8/1706185301473-b7155f04-3bb6-492b-b03f-ff97d4686d72.png 1576w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 590px) 100vw, 590px\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;opacity:0;transition:opacity 0.5s;color:inherit;box-shadow:inset 0px 0px 0px 400px white;top:0;left:0;\"\n        loading=\"lazy\"\n      />\n    </span>\n<a name=ZwFJZ></a></p>\n<h2>Code Mentor</h2>\n<p>有时候碰到技术问题解决不了，我也会在 Code Mentor 上寻求帮助。我发现在这上面找人聊天，一句废话都没有，全是直奔解决问题来的。我很喜欢！<br /><span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 590px; \"\n    >\n      <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 61.48648648648649%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block; transition: opacity 0.5s 0.5s; pointer-events: none;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"image.png\"\n        title=\"image.png\"\n        src=\"/static/f07c4e3ac48f1883e04b1f5743b2bfd0/fcda8/1706185812413-596e683b-c108-478b-b69d-4831c7778d2f.png\"\n        srcset=\"/static/f07c4e3ac48f1883e04b1f5743b2bfd0/12f09/1706185812413-596e683b-c108-478b-b69d-4831c7778d2f.png 148w,\n/static/f07c4e3ac48f1883e04b1f5743b2bfd0/e4a3f/1706185812413-596e683b-c108-478b-b69d-4831c7778d2f.png 295w,\n/static/f07c4e3ac48f1883e04b1f5743b2bfd0/fcda8/1706185812413-596e683b-c108-478b-b69d-4831c7778d2f.png 590w,\n/static/f07c4e3ac48f1883e04b1f5743b2bfd0/efc66/1706185812413-596e683b-c108-478b-b69d-4831c7778d2f.png 885w,\n/static/f07c4e3ac48f1883e04b1f5743b2bfd0/d56e1/1706185812413-596e683b-c108-478b-b69d-4831c7778d2f.png 1130w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 590px) 100vw, 590px\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;opacity:0;transition:opacity 0.5s;color:inherit;box-shadow:inset 0px 0px 0px 400px white;top:0;left:0;\"\n        loading=\"lazy\"\n      />\n    </span><br /><span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 590px; \"\n    >\n      <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 141.2162162162162%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block; transition: opacity 0.5s 0.5s; pointer-events: none;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"image.png\"\n        title=\"image.png\"\n        src=\"/static/9f6210227e3366ee247c6321e6773e3c/fcda8/1706185829938-317eb093-5d86-42ed-96f3-c40f6bad31d1.png\"\n        srcset=\"/static/9f6210227e3366ee247c6321e6773e3c/12f09/1706185829938-317eb093-5d86-42ed-96f3-c40f6bad31d1.png 148w,\n/static/9f6210227e3366ee247c6321e6773e3c/e4a3f/1706185829938-317eb093-5d86-42ed-96f3-c40f6bad31d1.png 295w,\n/static/9f6210227e3366ee247c6321e6773e3c/fcda8/1706185829938-317eb093-5d86-42ed-96f3-c40f6bad31d1.png 590w,\n/static/9f6210227e3366ee247c6321e6773e3c/be86f/1706185829938-317eb093-5d86-42ed-96f3-c40f6bad31d1.png 662w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 590px) 100vw, 590px\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;opacity:0;transition:opacity 0.5s;color:inherit;box-shadow:inset 0px 0px 0px 400px white;top:0;left:0;\"\n        loading=\"lazy\"\n      />\n    </span><br />除了键盘聊，还可以视频，只是有点废钱。\n<a name=n6P1W></a></p>\n<h1>开启字幕</h1>\n<p>现在的视频聊天软件，都有实时字幕功能。开启它，帮助理解。这在和口音非常严重的人交流时特别有帮助。<br /><span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 590px; \"\n    >\n      <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 8.108108108108107%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,iVBORw0KGgoAAAANSUhEUgAAABQAAAACCAYAAABYBvyLAAAACXBIWXMAABYlAAAWJQFJUiTwAAAAb0lEQVR42jWNSwpFIQxD724URPyAIH4Hjh0Iouj+95GHhTc4JLRN+iml8NBaE1JKGGPICyHAOSdSSphzoveOcw6x1qLZ3hv3Xowx8DnnkHNGjJFCIQS01lBKgbUWjDEqfE/e3nuPWivxcu/+6d//AE6ERDjrtAjaAAAAAElFTkSuQmCC'); background-size: cover; display: block; transition: opacity 0.5s 0.5s; pointer-events: none;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"image.png\"\n        title=\"image.png\"\n        src=\"/static/28707426e8d67239b273a4607b47edff/fcda8/1706183717429-7141cb72-6beb-4ad6-96f1-811a7699502e.png\"\n        srcset=\"/static/28707426e8d67239b273a4607b47edff/12f09/1706183717429-7141cb72-6beb-4ad6-96f1-811a7699502e.png 148w,\n/static/28707426e8d67239b273a4607b47edff/e4a3f/1706183717429-7141cb72-6beb-4ad6-96f1-811a7699502e.png 295w,\n/static/28707426e8d67239b273a4607b47edff/fcda8/1706183717429-7141cb72-6beb-4ad6-96f1-811a7699502e.png 590w,\n/static/28707426e8d67239b273a4607b47edff/efc66/1706183717429-7141cb72-6beb-4ad6-96f1-811a7699502e.png 885w,\n/static/28707426e8d67239b273a4607b47edff/f79fa/1706183717429-7141cb72-6beb-4ad6-96f1-811a7699502e.png 940w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 590px) 100vw, 590px\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;opacity:0;transition:opacity 0.5s;color:inherit;box-shadow:inset 0px 0px 0px 400px white;top:0;left:0;\"\n        loading=\"lazy\"\n      />\n    </span><br /><span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 590px; \"\n    >\n      <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 25%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block; transition: opacity 0.5s 0.5s; pointer-events: none;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"image.png\"\n        title=\"image.png\"\n        src=\"/static/a54a9a24642f5431478734329531a5c4/fcda8/1706183675904-79d6a2f7-2059-481c-9df9-b9fe82c61f39.png\"\n        srcset=\"/static/a54a9a24642f5431478734329531a5c4/12f09/1706183675904-79d6a2f7-2059-481c-9df9-b9fe82c61f39.png 148w,\n/static/a54a9a24642f5431478734329531a5c4/e4a3f/1706183675904-79d6a2f7-2059-481c-9df9-b9fe82c61f39.png 295w,\n/static/a54a9a24642f5431478734329531a5c4/fcda8/1706183675904-79d6a2f7-2059-481c-9df9-b9fe82c61f39.png 590w,\n/static/a54a9a24642f5431478734329531a5c4/efc66/1706183675904-79d6a2f7-2059-481c-9df9-b9fe82c61f39.png 885w,\n/static/a54a9a24642f5431478734329531a5c4/c83ae/1706183675904-79d6a2f7-2059-481c-9df9-b9fe82c61f39.png 1180w,\n/static/a54a9a24642f5431478734329531a5c4/73dae/1706183675904-79d6a2f7-2059-481c-9df9-b9fe82c61f39.png 2122w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 590px) 100vw, 590px\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;opacity:0;transition:opacity 0.5s;color:inherit;box-shadow:inset 0px 0px 0px 400px white;top:0;left:0;\"\n        loading=\"lazy\"\n      />\n    </span>\n<a name=tPiJa></a></p>\n<h1>AI 演讲教练</h1>\n<p>微软的 Teams 有虚拟的演讲教练，这真是很棒的功能。<br /><span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 508px; \"\n    >\n      <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 30.405405405405407%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block; transition: opacity 0.5s 0.5s; pointer-events: none;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"image.png\"\n        title=\"image.png\"\n        src=\"/static/160f7a28d03392a60925df2defe8fdd0/2fd48/1706183763120-bb8b186c-2ead-43f7-8ae0-bdb09ea5b993.png\"\n        srcset=\"/static/160f7a28d03392a60925df2defe8fdd0/12f09/1706183763120-bb8b186c-2ead-43f7-8ae0-bdb09ea5b993.png 148w,\n/static/160f7a28d03392a60925df2defe8fdd0/e4a3f/1706183763120-bb8b186c-2ead-43f7-8ae0-bdb09ea5b993.png 295w,\n/static/160f7a28d03392a60925df2defe8fdd0/2fd48/1706183763120-bb8b186c-2ead-43f7-8ae0-bdb09ea5b993.png 508w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 508px) 100vw, 508px\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;opacity:0;transition:opacity 0.5s;color:inherit;box-shadow:inset 0px 0px 0px 400px white;top:0;left:0;\"\n        loading=\"lazy\"\n      />\n    </span><br />每次在开完一个视频会议后，都可以看到反馈和待改进项，这可以帮助我进步！<br /><span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 590px; \"\n    >\n      <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 72.97297297297297%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block; transition: opacity 0.5s 0.5s; pointer-events: none;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"image.png\"\n        title=\"image.png\"\n        src=\"/static/155c4ac33f7e1660128aa29443b40f5d/fcda8/1706183943575-3b812a5c-a774-4bf0-b0b2-46b9d095229e.png\"\n        srcset=\"/static/155c4ac33f7e1660128aa29443b40f5d/12f09/1706183943575-3b812a5c-a774-4bf0-b0b2-46b9d095229e.png 148w,\n/static/155c4ac33f7e1660128aa29443b40f5d/e4a3f/1706183943575-3b812a5c-a774-4bf0-b0b2-46b9d095229e.png 295w,\n/static/155c4ac33f7e1660128aa29443b40f5d/fcda8/1706183943575-3b812a5c-a774-4bf0-b0b2-46b9d095229e.png 590w,\n/static/155c4ac33f7e1660128aa29443b40f5d/efc66/1706183943575-3b812a5c-a774-4bf0-b0b2-46b9d095229e.png 885w,\n/static/155c4ac33f7e1660128aa29443b40f5d/c83ae/1706183943575-3b812a5c-a774-4bf0-b0b2-46b9d095229e.png 1180w,\n/static/155c4ac33f7e1660128aa29443b40f5d/701e9/1706183943575-3b812a5c-a774-4bf0-b0b2-46b9d095229e.png 1780w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 590px) 100vw, 590px\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;opacity:0;transition:opacity 0.5s;color:inherit;box-shadow:inset 0px 0px 0px 400px white;top:0;left:0;\"\n        loading=\"lazy\"\n      />\n    </span><br />比如以上就是 AI 教练在一个站会后给我的反馈，说话时间一共是 1 分半钟，有 3 个问题需要改进，分别是：\n<a name=KakRu></a></p>\n<h2>不要总是说“啊、嗯”之类的停顿</h2>\n<p><span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 590px; \"\n    >\n      <span\n    clas